<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Please email <%= @unit_email %> or call the office at: <%= @contact_phone %> if you have any questions.
    </p>
    <p>Hello,</p>
    <p>
      This is a reminder of your upcoming reservation for today, <%= Date.today.strftime("%A, %d %B %Y")  %>  at <%= @start_time.partition(' ').last %> going to <%= @reservation.site.title %>.
      <br>Remember to fill out your Vehicle Report at the start of your trip. 
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <%= link_to "Modify or cancel your reservation", reservation_url(@reservation) %>
    </p>

    <p>
    Thank you,<br>
    Your <%= @reservation.program.unit.name %> RideShare Team
    </p>
    <p>
      Visit <%= link_to "LSA RideShare", all_root_url %> to view, modify, or cancel reservations.
    </p>
    <%= render 'garage_service' %> 
    <p>
      You are receiving this automated email because you are a driver in the LSA RideShare application.<br>
      <%= link_to "Unsubscribe", mailer_subscriptions_url %> from automated notifications.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
